It helps estimate revenue and pricing when accommodating large parties.

How it works:

- The value represents the expected spending per person per day for large group reservations
- It is used to calculate total revenue for group bookings and contributes to ASR metrics, helping
  track sales performance
- Helps provide accurate revenue projections based on reservation sizes

Example usage:

- If the value is set to 250 (representing $250 per person per day), and a large group reservation
  is made for 20 guests, the estimated revenue would be: `20 × $250 = $5000`""", "group": "5. Reports", "value_type": "number", "is_hidden": False }
)}}

